headline: North America Soy Protein Concentrate Market Report 2025-2034 | Government Support & Sustainable Innovations Drive Expansion
summary: The North America Soy Protein Concentrate Market, valued at USD 204.8 million in 2024, is projected to reach USD 508.8 million by 2034, growing at a 9.6% CAGR. This growth is driven by rising plant-based protein demand due to health trends and vegan diets. Soy protein concentrate, appreciated for its versatility and high protein content, is popular in nutraceuticals and meat substitutes.
